# Day 16 – Web Scraper with BeautifulSoup 🕸️

## What it does
Two scrapers built on the same day — one for Times of India,
one for Hacker News. Each fetches the top 10 headlines
and saves them to a headlines.txt file.

## Tech Stack
- Python 3
- requests
- BeautifulSoup4

## Setup
pip install requests beautifulsoup4

## How to run
python toi.py          # scrapes Times of India
python hackerwebsite.py   # scrapes Hacker News

## What I learned
- Sending requests with User-Agent headers
- Parsing HTML with BeautifulSoup
- find_all() with class selectors
- Deduplication with set()
- Saving scraped data to a text file

## Output
headlines.txt with top 10 numbered headlines
from the selected news source.
